ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 256, Quebec
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 256 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to QUEBEC with respect to the post-tropical storm Fiona that occurred from September 23 to 25, 2022.
